                                       java.lang.String[] permissions,

                                       int[] grantResults)
        Method is called by the Android framework when permission request result is returned.

        MissingPermission warnings are supressed, because if the code flow gets to the switch clause, we already have permissions. Otherwise the catch clause would be taken and method stopped earlier.
